overview:
Software development outsourcing company, based in Ukraine.

Rozdoum provides onshore and offshore software development, design and development of outsourced software product applications and services. Rozdoum domains are: model driven software development, e-commerce and e-marketing, global positioning and navigation systems, social networking, banking and insurance industry. We possess know-how in Java, J2EE, GMF, MDR, JMI, GEF, Eclipse, Hibernate, Spring, Webservices, SOAP, SOA, JSF, JSP.
